  "Name": "LOCATION_ITEM_BARCODE_ADJUSTMENT",
  "Description": "LOCATION_ITEM_BARCODE_ADJUSTMENT\n\nIf you need a system where users scan both the Location and MasterItem to identify the stock, thereby eliminating the need to print Tracking Entity barcodes. This process will use the barcode format of [LocationBarcode]_[MasterItemCode] to find the TrackingEntity.\n\nThis is one of potentially several processes you'll need to implement. All processes prefixed with LOCATION_ITEM_BARCODE_* are part of this implementation.",
